{"tid":2449813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大56%國民認同杯葛北京冬奧 中國超越俄羅斯成「美國最大敵人」","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T04:21:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"802f70d7e13d5e8212bf4f6cf070f583b3b8207e","tid":2449813,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"加拿大一項民調顯示，77%國民認為中國一日不釋放加拿大前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）和商人斯帕沃（Michael Spavor）， 兩國便不能保持友好關係；超過半數國民認為，當局明年應杯葛北京冬奧。加拿大主要盟友美國另一項民調指，中國已超越俄羅斯，成為美國最大敵人（U.S.&rsquo;s greatest enemy）。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大民調機構安格斯里德研究所（Angus Reid Institute）今年2月26日至3月3日，隨機訪問了5,004名加拿大國民，得出結果。調查發現，43%加拿大人非常認同（strongly agree）中國一日不釋放康明凱和斯帕沃， 加中兩國便不能保持友好關係；認同（agree）以上說法的加拿大人也有34%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/7Y6UJXS2FNDVHH5EA4HAVEPFZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2F7Y6UJXS2FNDVHH5EA4HAVEPFZI%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=feb297af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2F7Y6UJXS2FNDVHH5EA4HAVEPFZI%2F&h=402108d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/7Y6UJXS2FNDVHH5EA4HAVEPFZI/</a>"},{"pid":"e93b15fd7f39a3f098ad54f2279231e89ed71cd4","tid":2449813,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473d89597851c7fbd7f6411104f1a760d8488d8a","tid":2449813,"uid":71133,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">在共和黨人中，認為中國是美國最大敵人的比率高達76%；同類數字在民主黨人中僅得22%；在無政黨人士中則有43%。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢句先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd67c7dba92728637d645a02cfda4c0abffb3d7d","tid":2449813,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"473d89597851c7f